WEBVTT

00:00:00.507 --> 00:00:04.398
My big idea is a very, very small idea

00:00:04.422 --> 00:00:09.175
that can unlock billions of big ideas

00:00:09.199 --> 00:00:12.565
that are at the moment dormant inside us.

00:00:12.589 --> 00:00:16.003
And my little idea
that will do that is sleep.

00:00:16.437 --> 00:00:17.976
(Laughter)

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.213
(Applause)

00:00:22.237 --> 00:00:25.000
This is a room of type A women.

00:00:26.769 --> 00:00:29.858
This is a room of sleep-deprived women.